nett, Lynn; Prince, Clive (2006). <i>The Sion Revelation&#160;: The Truth about the Guardians of Christ's Sacred Bloodline</i>. New York, N.Y.: Touchstone books. pp.&#160;281\u201384. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780743263030\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780743263030\">9780743263030</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Sion+Revelation+%3A+The+Truth+about+the+Guardians+of+Christ%27s+Sacred+Bloodline.&amp;rft.place=New+York%2C+N.Y.&amp;rft.pages=281-84&amp;rft.pub=Touchstone+books&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.isbn=9780743263030&amp;rft.aulast=Picknett&amp;rft.aufirst=Lynn&amp;rft.au=Prince%2C+Clive&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALaurence+Gardner\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.entropic-art.com/book.html\">Entropic Fine Art Inc \u2013 Book</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20070505103651/http://www.entropic-art.com/book.html\">Archived</a> 5 May 2007 at the <a href=\"/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-king-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-king_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-king_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/g2/story/0,,308415,00.html\">The man who would be king</a>\u2014from The Guardian, 24 March 1999</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span